%% OSPP Error Recovery Flow — Station Reconnection After Disconnect
%% Reference: spec/04-flows.md, Section 9; examples/flows/10-error-recovery.md

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Station as ⚙️ Station
    participant Broker as 📡 MQTT Broker
    participant Server as 🖥️ Server

    Note over Station,Server: Normal operation — station connected, sessions active

    %% Disconnection
    rect rgb(255, 235, 238)
        Note over Station,Server: ⚠️ Connection Lost
        Station--xBroker: TCP connection drops
        Broker->>Server: ConnectionLost EVENT (LWT) [MSG-011]
        Server->>Server: Mark station offline<br/>Start recovery timer (300s)

        Note over Server: Server-side handling
        Server->>Server: Mark all bays as Unknown
        Server->>Server: Alert operators (push/email)
        Server->>Server: Suspend active sessions<br/>(grace period running)
    end

    %% Station buffers messages while offline
    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over Station: Station continues operating offline
        Station->>Station: Buffer MeterValues to persistent storage
        Station->>Station: Buffer StatusNotifications
        Station->>Station: Complete active sessions (if possible)
        Station->>Station: Buffer TransactionEvents
        Note over Station: Exponential backoff reconnection attempts<br/>1s → 2s → 4s → 8s → 16s → 30s cap
    end

    %% Reconnection
    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over Station,Server: ✅ Reconnection (e.g., after 45 seconds)
        Station->>Broker: MQTT CONNECT (mTLS, clean_start=false)
        Broker-->>Station: CONNACK (session present)

        %% Boot notification
        Station->>Broker: BootNotification REQUEST [MSG-001]
        Note right of Station: bootReason: "ErrorRecovery"<br/>pendingOfflineTransactions: 3
        Broker->>Server: BootNotification REQUEST
        Server-->>Broker: BootNotification RESPONSE (Accepted)
        Broker-->>Station: BootNotification RESPONSE
        Server->>Server: Cancel recovery timer<br/>Mark station online
    end

    %% Status reconciliation
    rect rgb(225, 245, 254)
        Note over Station,Server: Phase 1 — Status Reconciliation
        Station->>Broker: StatusNotification EVENT (Bay 1: Available)
        Broker->>Server: StatusNotification [MSG-009]
        Station->>Broker: StatusNotification EVENT (Bay 2: Available)
        Broker->>Server: StatusNotification [MSG-009]
        Station->>Broker: StatusNotification EVENT (Bay 3: Faulted)
        Broker->>Server: StatusNotification [MSG-009]
        Server->>Server: Reconcile bay states<br/>Resolve Unknown → actual state
    end

    %% Buffered message replay
    rect rgb(243, 229, 245)
        Note over Station,Server: Phase 2 — Buffered Message Replay (FIFO order)
        Station->>Broker: MeterValues EVENT (buffered, t=10:02:30)
        Broker->>Server: MeterValues [MSG-010]
        Station->>Broker: MeterValues EVENT (buffered, t=10:03:30)
        Broker->>Server: MeterValues [MSG-010]
        Station->>Broker: TransactionEvent REQUEST (offlineTxId, receipt, txCounter)
        Broker->>Server: TransactionEvent [MSG-007]
        Server->>Server: Validate receipt signature + txCounter sequence
        Server-->>Broker: TransactionEvent RESPONSE (Accepted)
        Broker-->>Station: TransactionEvent RESPONSE
    end

    Note over Station,Server: Station fully recovered — normal operation resumes
    Note over Server: Reconciliation complete<br/>Billing updated, operator notified
